{"tid":1681133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個 奶共偽人 （嚴選藍色偽人黑名單）","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:55:28.000Z","uid":333681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75bc7f81974b1e453013b99e79b83af953046a64","tid":1681133,"uid":333681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:31:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我先： 劉德華 - 唱 中國人/ 支持大嶼山填海</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然餐廳有黃藍 名單， 偽人都唔例外， 佢哋係香港出名， 不但冇利用自己影響力去支持運動外， 更加 因為奶共/大陸市場， 埋沒良知。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n把抗爭 融入生活， 罷睇 藍偽人演唱會/電視劇/電影， 既然佢地目光放在 大陸市場， 就令佢地 今生共享 大灣區榮耀， 香港市場 都唔需要佢地！！！"},{"pid":"cc7b9914ed64947c242488f598b1a1eef31cd9ab","tid":1681133,"uid":152108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:32:39.000Z","msg":"撐警陳百牆"},{"pid":"d5eee067008cc95d72087961b7361296488cb4bf","tid":1681133,"uid":193937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"魚民樂（元朗國）"},{"pid":"792d94e15ac35560752b2bf675696e187944512d","tid":1681133,"uid":150588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ezhc7G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ezhc7G.png&h=fab3e2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10d627ae50471a5742628dcdf2a6a6982f90c7c","tid":1681133,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。